headline: Emily Kaplan,  David Rosenberg
abstract: His frequent calls to his grandmothers got her thinking that he seemed like a real mensch.
lead_paragraph: Emily Alice Kaplan and David Zvi Rosenberg are to be married Jan. 19 at 99 Scott, an events space in Brooklyn. Rabbi Robert N. Levine is to officiate and lead the ceremony with Rabbi Dr. Reuven Leigh.
